// Web phase ↔ real chunks mapping:
//   Phase 1     = DONE (Phase 0 + 0bis + 0bis-bis + Phase 1 refactor → alpha)
//   Phase 2.0   = DONE (Sprint X-1 + 2.0a/b/c + 2.0c-bis Auth Path 2 → alpha.5)
//   Phase 2.1   = DONE (cleanup + 2.1.1 hardening + 2.1.2 soft-archiving + 2.x.1 search foundations → alpha.7→alpha.10)
//   Phase 2.2   = DONE (Plan bumps PR-1 serde_yml → alpha.10-bumps.1)
//   Phase 2.2.1 = IN PROGRESS (dual-write cohabitation acquired + notes organically migrated since 2026-05-09)
//   Phase 2.3   = DONE (PR-2/3/5/6 cumulative + 2.x.2 RRF + 2.x.3 Multi-Factor+Jina + 2.x.4 Endpoints → alpha.11→alpha.13 + alpha.12-bumps.1)
//   Phase 2.4   = TODO (production reranker — main.rs wiring + golden set + recall + ort 2.x stable)
//   Phase 2.5   = NEXT (End Double run — stop vault-mem secondary, gradatum single prod)
//   Phase 2.6   = NEXT (Gradatum Skills — reminder vault_search + memorize vault_write)
